{"tid":2101986,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［人生難題］外資大企文職位 vs 中小企對口位 應該點揀？","createTime":"2020-07-10T07:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T09:44:14.000Z","uid":256768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d97bc28a2f539cad90e1662bd0adc7eef7736d07","tid":2101986,"uid":256768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"本人讀BME，個牌唔入正苦基本冇乜用。宜加收到二隻offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外資大firm文職位：之前睇佢請人唔限科，所以掟左CV，點知得左。工作其實係Low-Skilled QA，暫時睇唔到有乜前景，亦都唔了解呢個industry。我個人覺得係個正常人都做到，至於拎offer就有個正常degree同個人smart 就可以。好處：做夠一年可以申請轉department 同放CV靚<br />\n<br />\n中小企港資對口position: 個title係international pre-sales engineer，因為我做唔到R&amp;D，所以呢份工好啱我。工作係將公司生產嘅devices做海外市場拓展同推廣，類似技術銷售。雖然未正式簽，但係可以學到野（例如knowledge of product &amp; Regulation of the medical devices) ，而且有成長空間。個未來director vision 都睇得遠（有whatsapp傾過）<br />\n<br />\n待遇上，外資無論係salary定welfare都好過中小企。但中小企有成長，啱自己條path。應該點揀？最近二三日要有決定，屋企人俾唔到有用嘅意見，盲叫我狗衝大企<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />衰在自己廢，offer少冇乜選擇。"},{"pid":"fc193112f4ff3cc322919842cb37cd57fb840c20","tid":2101986,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"外資<br />\n公司名靚跳糟都易<br />\n咁即係人工幾多"},{"pid":"e6a9cc5d9d6e79e4a2d3815f3a5773e482fa96ef","tid":2101986,"uid":256768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc193112f4ff3cc322919842cb37cd57fb840c20","tid":2101986,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"外資<br />\n公司名靚跳糟都易<br />\n咁即係人工幾多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:28:09.000Z","msg":"個basic其實差距1k左右，但大企仲有double pay，中小企冇。個1k係未計double"},{"pid":"21de32484c67bfb1ec2ba5b959377bc24fa82ca3","tid":2101986,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6a9cc5d9d6e79e4a2d3815f3a5773e482fa96ef","tid":2101986,"uid":256768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc193112f4ff3cc322919842cb37cd57fb840c20","tid":2101986,"